\v 2 Ngihlola, N\nd kosi\nd*, ungilinge\x + Hlab. 7.9. 17.3. 66.10. 139.23. Zek. 13.9.\x*, uhlole\x + Hlu. 7.4.\x* izinso zami lenhliziyo yami\x + Hlab. 7.9.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba uthandolomusa wakho luphambi kwamehlo ami, njalo ngihambe eqinisweni lakho\x + 2 Kho. 20.3. Hlab. 86.11.\x*.
