\v 4 Kangihlalanga\x + 26.5. Hlab. 1.1. Jer. 15.17.\x* labantu benkohliso\x + Jobe 11.11.\x*, kangihambelani labazenzisayo.
\v 5 Ngiyizondile inhlangano yabenzi bobubi\x + Hlab. 31.6. 139.21,22.\x*, kangihlali lababi\x + 26.5. Hlab. 1.1. Jer. 15.17.\x*.
\v 6 Ngizageza izandla zami ngokungelacala, ngizingelezele ilathi lakho, N\nd kosi\nd*\x + Hlab. 73.13. Eks. 30.19,20. Dute. 21.6. Hlab. 24.4.\x*.
\v 7 Ukuze ngizwakalise ngelizwi lokubonga\x + Neh. 12.42.\x*, lokuze ngilandise zonke izenzo zakho ezimangalisayo\x + Hlab. 9.1.\x*.
\v 8 N\nd kosi\nd*, ngiyayithanda inhlalo yendlu yakho\x + Hlab. 27.4.\x*, lendawo yokuhlala yenkazimulo yakho\x + Mat. 23.21.\x*.
\v 9 Ungabuthi umphefumulo wami kanye lezoni, kumbe impilo yami kanye labantu abomele igazi.
\v 10 Ozandla zabo zilobubi, lesandla sabo sokunene sigcwele izivalamlomo\x + Eks. 23.8.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa mina ngizahamba ngobuqotho bami; ngihlenga, ube lomusa kimi\x + 26.1.\x*.
\v 12 Unyawo lwami lumi endaweni elingeneyo\x + Hlab. 27.11.\x*; ngizayidumisa iN\nd kosi\nd* emabandleni\x + Hlab. 68.26. Hlab. 22.25.\x*.